{"tid":2415440,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬鎮壓奪命 少女中槍不治  示威勢升溫 撐軍僧侶襲民眾","createTime":"2021-02-20T08:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T14:25:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":122,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"de0502f1d14ff8fc212f4414068bd08e03c2ce58","tid":2415440,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210220/PZQ3WQU5PZGFJISWLXYDOWF5R4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210220%2FPZQ3WQU5PZGFJISWLXYDOWF5R4%2F&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbksdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=302f3c2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210220%2FPZQ3WQU5PZGFJISWLXYDOWF5R4%2F&h=c2191ea1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210220/PZQ3WQU5PZGFJISWLXYDOWF5R4/</a><br />\n<br />\n緬鎮壓奪命 少女中槍不治 <br />\n示威勢升溫 撐軍僧侶襲民眾<br />\n<br />\n上周被緬甸軍警開槍打中頭部重傷的女示威者，延醫至昨天不治，年僅20歲，成為當地月初政變首位亡魂和烈士，預料她的死訊會觸發全國新一輪反軍政府浪潮。不過，軍方並非完全孤立，一批相信同極端民族主義組織有關的緬僧，開始上街襲擊示威者。<br />\n<br />\n死者妙兌兌凱（Mya Thwate Thwate Khaing）是原國務資政昂山素姬的支持者，去年11月首次投票便是投給昂山領導的全國民主聯盟，豈料亦是最後一次。這位雜貨店女工上周二在首都內比都示威聲援被推翻的昂山素姬時，遇上軍警實彈鎮壓，頭部中槍危殆的她送院搶救，但當時醫生已不表樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SN6guS-E8IPw7ePfzmksYhoW9k4=/3150x2096/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5QO76NQOQZFY3HP47WDXB2KIDI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSN6guS-E8IPw7ePfzmksYhoW9k4%3D%2F3150x2096%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5QO76NQOQZFY3HP47WDXB2KIDI.jpg&h=6785c507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■仰光一處街頭成為悼念妙兌兌凱的地點。路透社<br />\n<br />\n妙兌兌凱的哥哥表示，家人早就擔心士兵會開殺戒，曾叮囑她勿在抗爭中走得太前，但最後她還是走在最前列，結果不幸一語成讖。妙兌兌凱中槍倒下的畫面，被印製成巨型海報，懸掛在全國最大城市仰光，成為了緬甸人反抗極權的象徵，如今她的死訊勢將進一步燃起民眾不滿政變的怒火。<br />\n<br />\n「我以她為榮，我會一直站出來，直至完成她的遺願為止。」24歲的仰光示威者尼林泰堅定地說。雖然軍方昨日全力封鎖市中心蘇雷寶塔附近一帶，試圖阻止示威者集結，卻出現群眾反包圍封鎖區的場面，一名示威者表示：「軍警害怕我們，不讓我們聚集唱歌，我們會繼續和平抗爭。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uFEjBokNJuae35IgAA4lbyWInwA=/1522x860/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/77DQKEYBANE65JVZRSDNKSFKME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuFEjBokNJuae35IgAA4lbyWInwA%3D%2F1522x860%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F77DQKEYBANE65JVZRSDNKSFKME.jpg&h=87ab7f7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■妙兌兌凱上周二參加示威被實彈射中，至昨日不治。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mXsrmOrY66B4CjOA4Cbxippc7VM=/1744x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NGKTE6BYZVHPDD32CJAAITF2AY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmXsrmOrY66B4CjOA4Cbxippc7VM%3D%2F1744x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNGKTE6BYZVHPDD32CJAAITF2AY.jpg&h=7c01c44e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■痛失女兒的敏姬（中）跌坐地上。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Zp9MNUSZPR3fkuPUFiIzuvewtCA=/1289x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3JSDBDNBEFB4TPGGP2ZA6YWI3I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZp9MNUSZPR3fkuPUFiIzuvewtCA%3D%2F1289x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3JSDBDNBEFB4TPGGP2ZA6YWI3I.jpg&h=a9e304b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■妙兌兌凱的遺體昨早被運離醫院。 路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n四分三公務員響應罷工<br />\n<br />\n可是，軍方也有知心友，近年一直支持出兵打擊少數民族分離運動的激進僧侶，前天突然在仰光街頭出現，他們持棍襲擊示威者，又打爛停泊在路邊「和你塞」的汽車，附近軍警見狀袖手旁觀。涉事僧侶得手遁回寺廟，趕至的民眾見裏面有士兵看守，一名僧人對外叫囂：「不要來跟我說甚麼公義，除非想我再打多你一頓。」<br />\n<br />\n自從示威者發起公民抗命運動以來，緬甸已有四分三公務員響應罷工，全國鐵路陷入癱瘓。聯合國人權問題特別報告員安德魯斯認為，現在正是。國際社會向軍政府進一步施壓的時候。繼美國之後，英國和加拿大前天也宣佈制裁軍政府領袖，凍結他們的資產和實施入境禁令。新加坡有供應反航拍機器材的公司，昨宣佈停止跟緬甸當局的交易。<br />\n<br />\n有緬甸民眾。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國《衞報》/《泰晤士報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f5fd3e8fc2b90e61fea665b0c2b736c2d3911a","tid":2415440,"uid":155095,"like":214,"dislike":1,"score":213,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:58:26.000Z","msg":"兇手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i9uNTfK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi9uNTfK.jpg&h=247fe7dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5fc9ae561975663213e0fb1e7b0d9bd10a13d37","tid":2415440,"uid":220451,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:59:13.000Z","msg":"天下黑驚一樣黑"},{"pid":"f7d315b0da62e026c27ba4685feb0c64c84cbf83","tid":2415440,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4fde9209d0b4fc030acc6cbb952530739bba60e","tid":2415440,"uid":329324,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"quote":{"pid":"49f5fd3e8fc2b90e61fea665b0c2b736c2d3911a","tid":2415440,"uid":155095,"like":214,"dislike":1,"score":213,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:58:26.000Z","msg":"兇手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i9uNTfK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi9uNTfK.jpg&h=247fe7dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:06:41.000Z","msg":"中國正一全球毒瘤"},{"pid":"81969e8680833f9d9ac497a47b2e12a6b7b0b07a","tid":2415440,"uid":107681,"like":31,"dislike":