6709954330638&h=3b588ff4\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/YourAnonCentral/status/1363096709954330638</a><br />\n射擊平民，無人機視角版<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/2021nam/status/1363126242665369604?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F2021nam%2Fstatus%2F1363126242665369604%3Fs%3D20&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbksdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=bc05429d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F2021nam%2Fstatus%2F1363126242665369604%3Fs%3D20&h=943fafe7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/2021nam/status/1363126242665369604?s=20</a><br />\n人群視角版，片中聽到有不少槍聲，然而不見軍隊有任何擋格動作<br />\n可以猜想是軍隊在向人民開槍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RFA_Chinese/status/1363122408446599174?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRFA_Chinese%2Fstatus%2F1363122408446599174%3Fs%3D20&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbksdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=e865c30f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRFA_Chinese%2Fstatus%2F1363122408446599174%3Fs%3D20&h=9a00c319\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RFA_Chinese/status/1363122408446599174?s=20</a><br />\n民眾家中拍攝版，拍攝者是一名驚慌的少女，她目睹緬甸軍人隨意槍殺平民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/mr-china-02172021073303.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fmr-china-02172021073303.html&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbksdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=cb8e36e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/mr-china-02172021073303.html</a><br />\n有網媒指中國一直供應武器俾緬軍，真假有待考究"},{"pid":"fadf139bf36aee7fd0cd54be5aeb7a6ec1e8a837","tid":2415440,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T15:16:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uT2Dhz9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuT2Dhz9.png&h=2c60bb66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/mrlamsan3\" data-sr-url=\"http